data.description: Beautiful and bright, newly updated 2-bedroom corner unit with its own parking space! New appliances include washer/dryer, ceiling fans, LED lighting. New kitchen is a dream with Samsung stainless steel smart appliances, gorgeous glass tile backsplash, oversized quartz kitchen countertops, and soft-close kitchen cabinets w/pullouts. New luxury vinyl plank flooring and professional paint throughout. Large closets in both bedrooms, spacious kitchen pantry, linen closet. Storage for rent on every floor. Furniture negotiable. Experience the feel of neighborhood living a few blocks from Waikiki Beach, across from the Ala Wai, close to restaurants, shops, parks, the Honolulu Zoo, and one block to the bus stop to catch a ride almost anywhere on the island. The WAIKIKI SKYLINER is a secure building with a secure garage & elevator, a live-in resident manager and private pool for residents. New custom window blinds, upgraded window screens, and great 90 sq.ft. lanai. Pet friendly (2 per unit). Concrete perimeter walls and cross breezes keep the unit comfortable almost year round. Move-in ready, this unit is remarkably comfortable and functional. VA Assumable Loan option at 3.375% available.
